Class TransferMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.plugins.mq.service.provider.TransferMessage

  • public class TransferMessage
extends Object
    Uniform representation of the message notion, to be used independently on any MQ implementation.

      • HEADER_TRUST_USER

        public static final String HEADER_TRUST_USER
        Boolean property on a JMS message, indicating that the user can be trusted and no password authentication within communote must be done. This is the case if the connection is using an embedded non network connection (e.g. vm protocol in activemq)
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • HEADER_PRE_AUTHENTICATED_USER_IDENTIFICATION

        public static final String HEADER_PRE_AUTHENTICATED_USER_IDENTIFICATION
        Header constant holding a user identification of a pre authenticated user. pre authentication means that the user has been authenticated through the message broker.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • HEADER_PRE_AUTHENTICATED_CLIENT_ID

        public static final String HEADER_PRE_AUTHENTICATED_CLIENT_ID
        Header constant corresponding to HEADER_PRE_AUTHENTICATED_USER_IDENTIFICATION. The value holds the client id the identification is valid for.

        Constant Field Values
